## What to do after a publish

1. Update this file with the publish date and platform.
2. Update `plans/NEXT.md` - remove the completed item, reorder what is left.
3. Update `context/HANDOFF.md` - log the publish.
4. Update `pipeline/pipeline_tracker.md` weekly metrics if it is the same week.
